-*- texinfo -*-
@deftypefn {Function File} {} nextpow2 (@var{x})
If @var{x} is a scalar, returns the first integer @var{n} such that
@iftex
@tex
 $2^n \ge |x|$.
@end tex
@end iftex
@ifinfo
 2^n >= abs (x).
@end ifinfo

If @var{x} is a vector, return @code{nextpow2 (length (@var{x}))}.
@seealso{pow2}
@end deftypefn
